{"tid":179564,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時開始的士佬做埋傳教仕","createTime":"2017-03-30T10:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T14:38:58.000Z","uid":1844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f264d3cb6c32d59387fb87e6da32e1d2d6493f44","tid":179564,"uid":1844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"岩岩係銅鑼灣上的士，一上的士就問我有無信教<br />\n我答無。 之後佢就話唔得架後生仔 要信教架，我笑左笑 點知佢一停紅燈就雙手舉起大叫耶蘇就係上帝 耶蘇替你死又替你復活 我即刻呆左以為自己入左邪教。 佢一路揸車一路另轉頭同我講耶蘇 幾驚佢撞 最後我頂唔順同佢講 如果你再另轉頭講耶蘇 我地就一齊去見耶蘇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。佢先認真返揸車。最後落車仲同我講 愿你信耶蘇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52493b0e1d9fe973e53b1765db0cfd0c1c0921c8","tid":179564,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"傳教士式"},{"pid":"0f49e23242c8130b87de82673930fd293ca90a4e","tid":179564,"uid":1844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"如果個個的士佬都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b8ef974fb919f3959874833e9b21795d43f087","tid":179564,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T10:45:24.000Z","msg":"屌 啲的士佬想吹下水姐"},{"pid":"7eafeeaf81fc3a59ac6ffc73e5ea9d746fbd97f7","tid":179564,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"嗌的士佬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\